4.3 Communications and Notices: All communications and notices between the Parties shall be made in writing and will be considered validly delivered under the following circumstances:

(i) Immediately upon delivery in person;
(ii) Ten (10) business days after being sent via registered or certified mail, return receipt requested, with postage prepaid;
(iii) On the next business day after being sent by FedEx or a similar internationally recognized overnight delivery service;
(iv) Within twenty-four (24) hours if delivered by facsimile or email, provided that a hard copy is also sent by one of the methods specified in (i), (ii), or (iii) within five (5) business days following the initial electronic transmission.
